{
  "texts": [
    "In order to mimic a true patient situation, cases were processed to patient layman language.",
    "Medical history was provided in first-person perspective, containing only general information and avoiding clinical expert terminology.",
    "Layman readability was independently checked by two non medical researchers and alternative laymen terms were provided if expert terminology was used.",
    "In cases of disagreement for laymen translation, consensus was achieved by a third non medical researcher.",
    "Querying GPT-3•5 and GPT-4"
  ]
}